---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '@fontsource-variable/inter';
import '@fontsource/plus-jakarta-sans';

const publishDate = new Date('2024-04-15');
const formattedDate = publishDate.toLocaleDateString('en-US', {
  year: 'numeric',
  month: 'long',
  day: 'numeric'
});
---

<Layout title="The Future of Sustainable Home Building - BORN">
  <article>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="relative h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center mb-16">
      <div class="absolute inset-0">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600585154526-990dced4db0d?auto=format&q=75&fit=crop&w=2000"
          alt="Sustainable Home"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center text-white px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center text-sm mb-6 space-x-4 font-medium">
          <time datetime={publishDate.toISOString()}>{formattedDate}</time>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By Sarah Johnson</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>5 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-6 leading-tight">
          The Future of Sustainable Home Building
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Discover how we are incorporating eco-friendly materials and renewable energy solutions in our newest developments.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Article Content -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 pb-20">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-primary-600 mb-12">
          As we move further into the 21st century, the importance of sustainable building practices cannot be overstated. At BORN, we're committed to leading the charge in eco-friendly home construction, implementing innovative solutions that not only benefit the environment but also provide long-term value to our homeowners.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl mb-6">Embracing Sustainable Materials</h2>
        <p>
          One of the fundamental shifts in our approach to home building has been the careful selection of sustainable materials. We're increasingly utilizing:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Recycled steel and aluminum for structural components</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Sustainably sourced timber from certified forests</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Low-carbon concrete alternatives</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Reclaimed materials where appropriate</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <!-- Rest of the sections with similar styling -->
        
        <blockquote class="my-12 pl-6 border-l-4 border-primary-600 italic text-xl text-primary-700">
          "At BORN, we believe that sustainable building practices are not just a trend but a necessity for the future of housing."
        </blockquote>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          By implementing these innovative solutions today, we're creating homes that will stand the test of time while minimizing their environmental impact.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Author Bio -->
      <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-primary-100">
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573496799652-408c2ac9fe98?auto=format&q=75&fit=crop&w=100"
            alt="Sarah Johnson"
            class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full object-cover mr-6"
          />
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg mb-2">Sarah Johnson</h3>
            <p class="text-primary-600 leading-relaxed">Head of Sustainability at BORN, with over 15 years of experience in sustainable architecture and eco-friendly construction practices.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Share Links -->
      <div class="mt-12 flex items-center justify-center space-x-6">
        <a href="#" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-900 transition-colors">
          Share on Twitter
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-900 transition-colors">
          Share on LinkedIn
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-900 transition-colors">
          Share on Facebook
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout> 